nResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='Waited for 5 seconds', extracted_content='Waited for 5 seconds', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='Extracted content from https://resy.com/resyos/ for query: Resy restaurant search page content\nContent saved to file system: Extracted content saved to file extracted_content_0.md successfully. and displayed in <read_state>.', extracted_content='<url>\nhttps://resy.com/resyos/\n</url>\n<query>\nResy restaurant search page content\n</query>\n<result>\nSign InSupportMake a ResyPlease Select LanguageUnited States (English)Canada (English)Canada (Français)\n****\nBook a Consultation\n  * Resy for Restaurants __\n    * Restaurant Solutions\n      * Maximize Your Revenue\n      * Streamline Your Operations\n      * Turn Guests Into Regulars\n    * Event Management\n    * Partnerships & Perks\n    * Integrations\n    * Resy x Amex Marketing Engine\n    * The Diner Experience\n  * The Resy x Amex Guest __\n    * Tap Our Guest Network\n    * Grow Your Dining Community\n  * Resy Resources __\n    * Restaurant Blog __\n    * In The News __\n    * Success Stories\n    * Special Events and Experiences\n    * Tips to Market your Restaurant\n  * Pricing\nBook a Consultation\n# Turn Reservations into\xa0Relationships\nJoin a community of passionate hospitality professionals who partner with Resy to help grow their business today and stay relevant tomorrow.\nBook a Consultation\n## Resy’s Top Features for\xa0Restaurants\n  * Flexible Reservations\n  * Event Management Tools\n  * Advanced Analytics\n  * POS Integration\n  * Guest Intel\n### Flexible Reservations\nManage bookings, help reduce no-shows, and maximize seating efficiency.\n  * Automated waitlists\n  * Real-time notifications\n  * Smart table optimization\nLearn More\n### Event Management Tools\nFrom private dinners to large celebrations, Resy has the tools to handle essential details.\n  * Customizable event pages\n  * Reservation tracking\n  * Integrated communication\nLearn More\n### Advanced Analytics\nTrack guest preferences and performance metrics using restaurant data analytics software to make more informed decisions.\n  * Guest data at your fingertips\n  * Cover count analysis\n  * VIP tracking\nLearn More\n### POS Integration\nStreamline operations by syncing your POS system with any of Resy OS Reservation plans to help enable data sharing.\n  * Real-time sales insights\n  * Integrated guest and payment data\n  * Enhanced reporting\nLearn More\n### Guest Intel\nOffer a tailored experience with Resy’s detailed guest intel and preference tracking.\n  * Track visit history\n  * Special occasion reminders\n  * Personal preferences\nLearn More\n## Why Restaurants Choose Resy\n### Optimize Operations with\xa0Flexible Reservations\nHelp turn more tables with tools that reduce no-shows and streamline bookings.\n### Backed by American Express\nAs an American Express company, Resy provides direct access to high-spending Card Members.\n### Event Management\nPlan, manage, and promote events that can drive additional revenue, all through one platform.\n### Data-Driven Insights\nUse Resy’s advanced analytics to make more informed business decisions.\n### Guest Experience, Enhanced\nElevate your service with personalized intel and make every guest feel like a VIP.\n## Meet the Resy Guest\nResy Guests are engaged diners who love discovering new restaurants. Whether they’re American Express® Card Members or other Resy users, these guests value high-quality dining experiences and are eager to explore new restaurants. Learn more about who dines with Resy.\n  * **4x**\nAmerican Express® Card Members book 4x more reservations than non-American Express Card Members.1\n  * **60%**\nMore than 60% of Resy users are repeat guests.2\n  * **92%**\nThe average annual dining spend for American Express Card Members with a Resy account is 92% higher than that of American Express Card Members who do not have a Resy account.3\n  * **3.49%**\nResy guests have an average no-show rate of 3.49%.4\nLearn More\n### Resy and American Express Drive Demand\nFind out how Resy helps you fill seats and reach diners. With access to American Express® Card Members and powerful demand generation tools, we can bring more guests to your restaurant, helping you grow your business.\nLearn More\n## What Restaurants Are Saying About Resy\nDon’t just take our word for it—check out what restaurants are saying about how Resy has helped them fill tables, streamline operations, and build stronger relationships with their guests.5\n> "“Resy has quickly become the industry standard. It\'s intuitive and well known by guests.”"**Semma, Dhamaka, Adda, Masalawala & Sons, Naks  \n>  (Unapologetic Foods),** New York\n> "“Resy’s commitment to partnership has made a tremendous and valuable change in our business, and their personal attention has been unmatched.”"**Boia De,** Miami\n> "“Resy has user-friendly technology with wonderful support from our Resy rep when we have any type of question. We were lucky to be featured in Resy articles which guests have mentioned to us, so they\'re definitely reading the content! I also love the online articles/resources for restaurant owners and operators.”"**Baroo,** Los Angeles\n> "“Resy has continued to go above and beyond in answering tech questions, promoting our events, and creating solutions to our specific needs. Our account manager never hesitates to set up a phone call or video chat to answer questions or just brainstorm ideas of how we can use Resy to better our business.”"**Lucian,** Atlanta\n> "“Resy allows me to manage the parts of restaurant life that traditionally required restaurant operators to be chained to their brick and mortar locations from the comfort of my home and always at my fingertips. The ability to manage and edit reservations in real time is life changing.”"**Maxwells Trading,** Chicago\nPreviousNext\n### Trusted by respected and beloved restaurants\n  *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   * \n  *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   *   * \n _Pause animation_ _Run animation_Book a Consultation\n## Stay Informed with the Latest Insights from Resy’s Restaurant Blog, On The House\nExplore industry best practices, thought leadership, and real-world examples of how restaurants are using Resy to thrive.  \nCheck out our latest blog posts for tips and trends that help you grow your business.6\n### Four Tips to Help Boost Takeout Revenue Through the End of Winter\nRead more __\n### Five Wishes For 2024 From the Restaurant Industry\nRead more __\n### See How These Restaurants Use Add-On Items to Increase Their Earnings\nRead more __\n### Four Simple Steps to Make Your Restaurant More Sustainable\nRead more __\nView the Blog\n## Frequently Asked Questions\n  * What is Resy, and how does it help my restaurant?__\nResy is a restaurant management platform that helps you optimize reservations, reduce no-shows, enhance guest experiences, and streamline operations. With the powerful backing of American Express, Resy connects you with high-value guests to help fill your tables.\n  * How do I request a consultation to learn more about Resy?__\nYou can learn more by clicking the "Book a Consultation" button at the top of the page or by filling out the form on our homepage. Our team will get in touch to show you how Resy can benefit your restaurant.\n  * What kind of data does Resy provide to restaurants?__\nResy’s analytics include guest preferences, dining history, and booking patterns. This helps you tailor the dining experience and make informed business decisions.\n  * Does Resy integrate with POS systems?__\nYes!All Resy OS reservation plans integrate with the most utilized POS systems, allowing data sharing for smoother operations and enhanced guest management.\n## Ready to join us?  \nRight this way®\nResy and American Express help keep your tables booked and your seats filled with dedicated diners. We help grow your revenue, streamline your operations, and empower you to provide a consistently exceptional guest experience.\n### Book Your Resy Consultation Today\n* denotes required fields\nStep 1 of 2\nFirst Name*\nLast Name*\nEmail*\nMobile Phone*\nRestaurant Name*\nNext Step\n __Back\nPostal Code*\nCountry*Please SelectAland IslandsAlbaniaAlgeriaAndorraAngolaAnguillaAntarcticaAntigua and BarbudaArgentinaArmeniaArubaAustraliaAustriaAzerbaijanBahamasBahrainBangladeshBarbadosBelarusBelgiumBelizeBeninBermudaBhutanBolivia, Plurinational State ofBonaire, Sint Eustatius and SabaBosnia and HerzegovinaBotswanaBouvet IslandBrazilBritish Indian Ocean TerritoryBrunei DarussalamBulgariaBurkina FasoBurundiCambodiaCameroonCanadaCape VerdeCayman IslandsCentral African RepublicChadChileChinaChinese TaipeiChristmas IslandCocos (Keeling) IslandsColombiaComorosCongoCongo, the Democratic Republic of theCook IslandsCosta RicaCote d\'IvoireCroatiaCubaCuraçaoCyprusCzech RepublicDenmarkDjiboutiDominicaDominican RepublicEcuadorEgyptEl SalvadorEquatorial GuineaEritreaEstoniaEthiopiaFalkland Islands (Malvinas)Faroe IslandsFijiFinlandFranceFrench GuianaFrench PolynesiaFrench Southern TerritoriesGabonGambiaGeorgiaGermanyGhanaGibraltarGreeceGreenlandGrenadaGuadeloupeGuatemalaGuernseyGuineaGuinea-BissauGuyanaHaitiHeard Island and McDonald IslandsHoly See (Vatican City State)HondurasHungaryIcelandIndiaIndonesiaIran, Islamic Republic ofIraqIrelandIsle of ManIsraelItalyJamaicaJapanJerseyJordanKazakhstanKenyaKiribatiKorea, Democratic People\'s Republic ofKorea, Republic ofKuwaitKyrgyzstanLao People\'s Democratic RepublicLatviaLebanonLesothoLiberiaLibyan Arab JamahiriyaLiechtensteinLithuaniaLuxembourgMacaoMacedonia, the former Yugoslav Republic ofMadagascarMalawiMalaysiaMaldivesMaliMaltaMartiniqueMauritaniaMauritiusMayotteMexicoMoldova, 